{"surah":{"number":81,"name":"التكوير","englishName":"At-Takwir","englishTranslation":"The Overthrowing","ayahCount":29},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:40.458Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلشَّمْسُ","english":"the sun","translit":"l-shamsu","root":"شمس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كُوِّرَتْ","english":"is wrapped up","translit":"kuwwirat","root":"كور"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And when the stars fall, dispersing,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنُّجُومُ","english":"the stars","translit":"l-nujūmu","root":"نجم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱنكَدَرَتْ","english":"fall, losing their luster","translit":"inkadarat","root":"كدر"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And when the mountains are removed","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالُ","english":"the mountains","translit":"l-jibālu","root":"جبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُيِّرَتْ","english":"are moved away","translit":"suyyirat","root":"سير"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And when full-term she-camels are neglected","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْعِشَارُ","english":"the full-term she-camels","translit":"l-ʿishāru","root":"عشر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عُطِّلَتْ","english":"(are) left untended","translit":"ʿuṭṭilat","root":"عطل"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And when the wild beasts are gathered","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْوُحُوشُ","english":"the wild beasts","translit":"l-wuḥūshu","root":"وحش"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حُشِرَتْ","english":"are gathered","translit":"ḥushirat","root":"حشر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And when the seas are filled with flame","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْبِحَارُ","english":"the seas","translit":"l-biḥāru","root":"بحر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُجِّرَتْ","english":"are made to overflow","translit":"sujjirat","root":"سجر"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And when the souls are paired","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنُّفُوسُ","english":"the souls","translit":"l-nufūsu","root":"نفس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"زُوِّجَتْ","english":"are paired","translit":"zuwwijat","root":"زوج"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْءُۥدَةُ","english":"the female infant buried alive","translit":"l-mawūdatu","root":"وأد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُئِلَتْ","english":"is asked","translit":"su-ilat","root":"سأل"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"For what sin she was killed","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بِأَىِّ","english":"For what","translit":"bi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذَنۢبٍۢ","english":"sin","translit":"dhanbin","root":"ذنب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قُتِلَتْ","english":"she was killed","translit":"qutilat","root":"قتل"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And when the pages are made public","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلصُّحُفُ","english":"the pages","translit":"l-ṣuḥufu","root":"صحف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نُشِرَتْ","english":"are laid open","translit":"nushirat","root":"نشر"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"And when the sky is stripped away","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the sky","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كُشِطَتْ","english":"is stripped away","translit":"kushiṭat","root":"كشط"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And when Hellfire is set ablaze","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَحِيمُ","english":"the Hellfire","translit":"l-jaḥīmu","root":"جحم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُعِّرَتْ","english":"is set ablaze","translit":"suʿʿirat","root":"سعر"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And when Paradise is brought near,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةُ","english":"Paradise","translit":"l-janatu","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُزْلِفَتْ","english":"is brought near","translit":"uz'lifat","root":"زلف"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"A soul will [then] know what it has brought [with it].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلِمَتْ","english":"Will know","translit":"ʿalimat","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْسٌۭ","english":"a soul","translit":"nafsun","root":"نفس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّآ","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَحْضَرَتْ","english":"it has brought","translit":"aḥḍarat","root":"حضر"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"So I swear by the retreating stars -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَآ","english":"But nay","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أُقْسِمُ","english":"I swear","translit":"uq'simu","root":"قسم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْخُنَّسِ","english":"by the retreating planets","translit":"bil-khunasi","root":"خنس"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"Those that run [their courses] and disappear -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلْجَوَارِ","english":"Those that run","translit":"al-jawāri","root":"جري"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْكُنَّسِ","english":"(and) disappear","translit":"l-kunasi","root":"كنس"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"And by the night as it closes in","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّيْلِ","english":"And the night","translit":"wa-al-layli","root":"ليل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَسْعَسَ","english":"it departs","translit":"ʿasʿasa","root":"عسعس"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"And by the dawn when it breathes","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلصُّبْحِ","english":"And the dawn","translit":"wal-ṣub'ḥi","root":"صبح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَنَفَّسَ","english":"it breathes","translit":"tanaffasa","root":"نفس"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"[That] indeed, the Qur'an is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, it","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَقَوْلُ","english":"(is) surely a word","translit":"laqawlu","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَسُولٍۢ","english":"(of) a Messenger","translit":"rasūlin","root":"رسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَرِيمٍۢ","english":"noble","translit":"karīmin","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"[Who is] possessed of power and with the Owner of the Throne, secure [in position],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذِى","english":"Possessor of","translit":"dhī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قُوَّةٍ","english":"power","translit":"quwwatin","root":"قوي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِندَ","english":"with","translit":"ʿinda","root":"عند"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِى","english":"(the) Owner of","translit":"dhī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْعَرْشِ","english":"the Throne","translit":"l-ʿarshi","root":"عرش"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَكِينٍۢ","english":"secure","translit":"makīnin","root":"مكن"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"Obeyed there [in the heavens] and trustworthy.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مُّطَاعٍۢ","english":"One to be obeyed","translit":"muṭāʿin","root":"طوع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمَّ","english":"and","translit":"thamma","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَمِينٍۢ","english":"trustworthy","translit":"amīnin","root":"أمن"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"And your companion is not [at all] mad.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَاحِبُكُم","english":"(is) your companion","translit":"ṣāḥibukum","root":"صحب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِمَجْنُونٍۢ","english":"mad","translit":"bimajnūnin","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"And he has already seen Gabriel in the clear horizon.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","english":"And certainly","translit":"walaqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَءَاهُ","english":"he saw him","translit":"raāhu","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْأُفُقِ","english":"in the horizon","translit":"bil-ufuqi","root":"أفق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمُبِينِ","english":"the clear","translit":"l-mubīni","root":"بين"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And Muhammad is not a withholder of [knowledge of] the unseen.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"he (is)","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبِ","english":"the unseen","translit":"l-ghaybi","root":"غيب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِضَنِينٍۢ","english":"a withholder","translit":"biḍanīnin","root":"ضنن"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"And the Qur'an is not the word of a devil, expelled [from the heavens].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"it","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِقَوْلِ","english":"(is the) word","translit":"biqawli","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"شَيْطَـٰنٍۢ","english":"(of) Shaitaan","translit":"shayṭānin","root":"شطن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَّجِيمٍۢ","english":"accursed","translit":"rajīmin","root":"رجم"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"So where are you going?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَيْنَ","english":"So where","translit":"fa-ayna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَذْهَبُونَ","english":"are you going","translit":"tadhhabūna","root":"ذهب"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"It is not except a reminder to the worlds","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنْ","english":"Not","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"it","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"(is) except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِكْرٌۭ","english":"a reminder","translit":"dhik'run","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","english":"to the worlds","translit":"lil'ʿālamīna","root":"علم"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"For whoever wills among you to take a right course.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِمَن","english":"For whoever","translit":"liman","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"شَآءَ","english":"wills","translit":"shāa","root":"شيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","english":"among you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","english":"to","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَسْتَقِيمَ","english":"take a straight way","translit":"yastaqīma","root":"قوم"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"And you do not will except that Allah wills - Lord of the worlds.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَشَآءُونَ","english":"you will","translit":"tashāūna","root":"شيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَشَآءَ","english":"wills","translit":"yashāa","root":"شيأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَبُّ","english":"Lord","translit":"rabbu","root":"ربب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","english":"(of) the worlds","translit":"l-ʿālamīna","root":"علم"}]}]}
